      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation geometry and fluid properties must be representative of the COU device and blood rheology at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the same geometry used in the COU simulations. Blood was modeled as a non-Newtonian fluid using the Carreau-Yasuda viscosity model with parameters derived from literature hematocrit values representative of CPB conditions."
    },
